name: Wc-wallet
body:
#WooCommerce wallet / WC Wallet plugin
This plugin is created with the aim of refunding the cart total as the credits for the user and the user can use those credits for future cart and make order again.
The add money to wallet is under development. If wanted you can use this.
-Thank you
